    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">For the complete error gradient to vanish, all of these T sub gradients need to vanish. If we think of (3) as a series of functions, then by definition, this series converges to zero if the sequence of its partial sums tends to zero, so</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
